    <p>This scheme pro­vides crim­i­nal legal as­sis­tance to peo­ple who face charges in a Sin­ga­pore court for spec­i­fied of­fences where pun­ish­ments do not in­clude the death penalty. The scheme cov­ers of­fences in­clud­ing those un­der the Pe­nal Code, Mis­use of Drugs Act, Women’s Char­ter, and Preven­tion of Cor­rup­tion Act, among oth­ers.</p>


